{"tid":1562530,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「分析」如何令 人 做一個行為或者動作","createTime":"2019-09-12T04:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T04:56:59.000Z","uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"65bb491946b5235bd803d94fc33e57b95dc82940","tid":1562530,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:54:14.000Z","msg":"近排有好多post 要求大家做某樣事情<br />\n例如：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">捐錢，文宣，跳閘，國際宣傳等等</span></span><br />\n有啲好<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">成功</span></span> 但有啲相對<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">失敗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我觀察到 好多發起人嘗試以該<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">行動效益</span></span> 來說服其他人參與 但除咗效益之外 其實仲有一樣更重要既野要考慮<br />\n<br />\n就係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">方便同容易</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n捐錢，眾籌成功，係因為只要用電話上網就捐到，如果換成要去銀行捐，一定無咁成功。<br />\n<br />\n好少人做設計文宣，因為要有相當既技能先做到。相對，派文宣人人都可以做，自然多人做。但人手派又會少過airdrop派，因為後者更<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">容易方便</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n又例如跳閘，因為需要跳，又要唔怕俾人眼超超，又怕俾人捉，所以少人做，啲人會選擇俾錢過，係因為俾錢只要拎個銀包出黎就得，更<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">方便容易</span></span>。<br />\n但用綠卡又會多啲人做，因為相對跳閘，係更<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">容易</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n所以，如果要令人做一個動作，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請先考慮方唔方便同容唔容易</span></span>，而唔係第一時間諗效益效果。"},{"pid":"9a59bcf7ce523f6d05145a8aa461df055b6aef7d","tid":1562530,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:54:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"6d2d5c295faeffa3e511f4dff14dc521169e3b30","tid":1562530,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:55:13.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"7a5abe0339726ae3fc4ded0b3d544355962b6768","tid":1562530,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:55:25.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"5ce76783d4b5cfc7f8c60f026a350f8215bec7d2","tid":1562530,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:55:36.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"8758e22eaf2f4dae4f851ed19f0195d85b8ee310","tid":1562530,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:55:46.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"b2c5116c976010ff3540bcc3859d84a105151382","tid":1562530,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:55:58.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"13dcd4789f15eaefefc2786f257e8241d73aefdb","tid":1562530,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:56:11.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"e15e9dad69f8886526ef274689f688adee25c914","tid":1562530,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:56:25.000Z","msg":"推7"},{"pid":"56ccd956bda4daa112452add5cf1b2a85eeb6186","tid":1562530,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:56:36.000Z","msg":"推8"},{"pid":"d35a826275e4b32061df0f58fe77dd0f0e5658a7","tid":1562530,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:56:46.000Z","msg":"推9"},{"pid":"91f3367e942905426f013403bb04c31ce6e50951","tid":1562530,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:56:59.000Z","msg":"推10"}]}